          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "救你急救你恙救你贫困，"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "全你义全你节全你婚姻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我岂肯破人婚落个骂名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，人生在世，全被这金银累极了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "梆子导板",
          "musical_style": "梆子导板",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "杨五郎闻此言把头低下，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（垛板） 止不住泪珠儿点点如麻。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀来杀去杀杨家。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "箭箭射的白莲花。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要把金刀来削头发。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "脱却紫袍换袈裟。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣要到五台去出家。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿要上五台去出家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵呵，再来唱个侠义英雄，大闹忠义堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，我好悔也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "俺李逵做事太莽撞，"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "也不知是何人假扮了俺的大哥真宋江。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "俺李逵一闻此言怒满在胸膛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "砍倒了替天行道的杏黄旗，大闹忠义堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "难免李逵闹遭殃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "反被众人笑一场。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，待我再来学一个贞烈春娥教子成名的故事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "小奴才一句话问住了我，"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "闭口无言王氏春娥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "想起了亡故夫薛子辂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "等候了苦命妻一路同行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一遍一遍，一遍遍的诉夫听着，我那去世的夫吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再来学个汉朝吕后，欲谋刘氏之基业故事耳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "小奴才被我脸唬红，"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "拿本经史当卷宗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "夫人与我掌红灯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "剑斩白蛇路途中。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "二排写的是吕正宫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "关中十王一派宗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "赵皇娘名节存卷中。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，我曾听见过朱素云唱的《辕门射戟》，我来学学看。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（范陶亮嗓子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "看过了花笺纸二张，"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "手提着羊毫写几行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "纪将军台前问安康："
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "二非是待客似孟尝；"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "军机大事有商量。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "拜上使君要赏光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "有甚大事某承当。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "明日席前做商量。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我再学个狠心毒妇。列位晓得是谁？乃是隋朝节度使辛文礼之嫡妻，叫什么东"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方氏的，她见了好面孔，她就动了心了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在阵前闪出了伯党小将，"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "他赛如当年的潘安容妆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "赛吕布，赛吕布缺少了画杆戟枪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "与你来商量："
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我与你做夫妻地久天长。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，还有一出《酒醉杨贵妃》，没有串来。呵呵，险些儿忘了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哙，烦你几位当场面的老板，替我吹起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吹腔尾声） 去也，去也，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回宫去也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "辜负好良霄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "范陶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吹腔尾声） 只落得冷清清，独自回宫去也。"
        }
      ],
